
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPPERCASE Conventional Commits — Content Workspace
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Format:
#   TYPE(scope): description
#
#   [optional body]
#
#   [optional footer(s)]
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TYPE (required, UPPERCASE) — pick one:
#
#   CONTENT   New or updated vault content (notes, pages)
#   DOCS      Changes to documentation or guides
#   FIX       Corrections to existing content (typos, broken links)
#   REFACTOR  Reorganization without changing meaning (moves, renames)
#   CHORE     Maintenance (templates, folder org, vault config)
#   META      Changes to vault infrastructure (.obsidian, .claude, .gitignore)
#   STYLE     Formatting changes only (no content change)
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SCOPE (optional) — area of vault affected:
#   e.g., (inbox), (templates), (archive), (config)
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BODY (optional) — explain what and why, not how.
#   Separate from description with a blank line.
#
# FOOTER (optional) — references:
#   e.g., Closes #42
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI ATTRIBUTION
#
# Include these lines ONLY when applicable:
#
#   🤖 Generated with [Tool Name]
#     → Include when AI generated the commit MESSAGE
#     → Examples:
#       🤖 Generated with Claude Code
#       🤖 Generated with GitHub Copilot
#
#   Co-Authored-By: [Tool and Model] <noreply@provider.com>
#     → Include when AI helped generate the CODE/CHANGES
#     → Examples:
#       Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
#       Co-Authored-By: GitHub Copilot <noreply@github.com>
#
# Rules:
#   - AI wrote both message AND content  → include BOTH lines
#   - AI wrote message, human wrote content → include 🤖 line only
#   - Human wrote message, AI wrote content → include Co-Authored-By only
#   - No AI involvement                    → include neither
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
